# time_s colorbalance rs GS bs (gs in caps to mark channel — actual filter uses gs)
0.0 colorbalance rs 0.100000|gs 0.000000|bs -0.100000;
1.0 colorbalance rs 0.075000|gs 0.000000|bs -0.075000;
2.0 colorbalance rs 0.012500|gs 0.000000|bs -0.012500;
3.0 colorbalance rs -0.026667|gs 0.006667|bs 0.033333;
